Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:34.83,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}转呀转 旋转木马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:39.32,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}想要传达 却传达不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:44.08,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}重叠之日何时会到来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:49.96,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}希望你也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:19:04.44,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}像甜甜圈的正中间一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:12.32,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}本以为在这里却不在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:18.01,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}越是甜蜜 越想窥视
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:25.96,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}随意坐上去的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.19,0:19:28.14,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}铃声响起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:29.92,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}我注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.92,0:19:32.24,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只在远处看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:34.92,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为会晕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:38.68,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}闪闪发光 轻轻漂浮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:43.36,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}接近 又远离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:48.19,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你全身心地投入着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.86,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又像是会消失一般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:54.88,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}转呀转 旋转木马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:59.40,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}这个特别的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:03.87,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}现在还觉得挺舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.87,0:20:09.26,IN CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你是怎么想的呢
